<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-1">
        <i class="fa fa-exclamation-triangle fa-5x"></i>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-11">
        <h1 class="page-header">An error has occurred.</h1>
        {{#if networkError}}
            <p>arkOS encountered a problem in communicating with the server. There may have been an interruption in your network. Please try again by refreshing the page or physically checking the status of your server.</p>
            <a href="#" class="btn btn-default" onclick="document.location.reload();return false"><i class="fa fa-refresh"></i> Refresh page</a>
        {{else}}
            <p>arkOS encountered an error when trying to perform your last requested operation, and it cannot continue with it.</p>

            <h3>You can try again...</h3>
            <p>...by refreshing the page. In some cases, restarting the server or clearing your browser's cache may also help.</p>
            <div class="btn-group">
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-default" onclick="document.location.reload();return false"><i class="fa fa-refresh"></i> Refresh page</a>
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-default" {{action "reboot"}}><i class="fa fa-refresh"></i> Restart server</a>
            </div>
            
            <h3>Still having trouble?</h3>
            <p>If you think this is a bug, please let us know about the problem by automatically submitting a crash report. You can also manually do this by <a href="https://git.coderouge.co/arkOS/genesis/issues">filing an issue to our tracker</a>. Please make sure to include the full crash report when filing manually.</p>
            <div class="btn-group">
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-default" id="reportbtn" {{action "submitCrashReport"}}><i class="fa fa-bug"></i> Submit crash report</a>
                {{#if showingStacktrace}}
                {{else}}
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-default" {{action "showStacktrace"}}><i class="fa fa-search"></i> View stacktrace</a>
                {{/if}}
                {{#if showingCrashReport}}
                {{else}}
                <a href="#" class="btn btn-default" {{action "showCrashReport"}}><i class="fa fa-search"></i> Show full crash report</a>
                {{/if}}
            </div>
            
            {{#if showingCrashReport}}
                {{textarea class="form-control" rows=15 value=crashReport}}
            {{/if}}
            {{#if showingStacktrace}}
                {{textarea class="form-control" rows=15 value=stackTrace}}
            {{/if}}
        {{/if}}
    </div>
</div>
